title: Railworks TS2014 SSS Stanier 8F Collection Part 1
description:
This pack is a mega pack full of brand new liveries for the Woodhead 8F - including 3 variations of LMS, two LNER and 3 variations of BR livery. Also, various states of weathering are applied to these loco's as well. The CJB advanced steam effects and SSS sounds are applied to all these new liveries too. Weathered 21 Ton hopper wagons with custom sounds are also included and two scenario's.




Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


Please use the email address or the facebook fanpage for requests, questions and also if you want to share an addon with the community which we will post on your behalf.

If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.




A Team tpb_4_ever upload.
